      <h4>Specific Risks:</h4>
      <ul>
        <li>Text chat in public lobbies with strangers</li>
        <li>Inappropriate usernames and chat messages</li>
        <li>Accusations and social pressure</li>
        <li>External voice chat on Discord (higher risk)</li>
      </ul>

      <h4>Safety Settings:</h4>
      <ul>
        <li>Play in private lobbies with known friends only</li>
        <li>Use censored chat filter (but not foolproof)</li>
        <li>Report inappropriate names and behavior</li>
        <li>Disable guest mode to require account (creates accountability)</li>
